<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV54">
<l>ilaittalaicca ranturanti laṅkaikaṭṭa ḻittavaṉ</l>
<l>malaittalaippi ṟantiḻintu vantununtu cantaṉaṅ</l>
<l>kulaittalaitti ṟutteṟinta kuṅkumakku ḻampiṉō</l>
<l>ṭalaittoḻuku kāviriya raṅkamēya vaṇṇalē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who ruined Laṅkā by shooting an arrow [with] a leaf[-like] tip</l>
<l>is the Lord who dwells in Raṅgam by the Kāverī, which, being born in the mountain,</l>
<l>comes descending, casts sandalwood trees [ashore],</l>
<l>and flows dashing [against the shores] with the paste emitted by the Kamela trees</l>
<l rend="indent">that it had scattered, shaken, and broken.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
